#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "ketchup"
msgid_plural "ketchups"
msgstr[0] "番茄酱"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ketchup'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Good old ketchup, tastes great on hot dogs. This is a commercial version "
"specifically engineered for long shelf life, so it has a lot of "
"preservatives, artificial coloring, and flavoring."
msgstr "经典番茄酱，配热狗味道绝佳。这是专为长保质期设计的商业版本，因此含有大量防腐剂、人工色素和调味剂。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "mayonnaise"
msgid_plural "mayonnaise"
msgstr[0] "蛋黄酱"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mayonnaise', 'str_pl': 'mayonnaise'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Good old mayo, tastes great on sandwiches. This is a commercial version "
"specifically engineered for long shelf life, so it has a lot of "
"preservatives, artificial coloring, and flavoring."
msgstr "经典蛋黄酱，配三明治味道绝佳。这是专为长保质期设计的商业版本，因此含有大量防腐剂、人工色素和调味剂。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "ranch dressing"
msgid_plural "ranch dressing"
msgstr[0] "牧场沙拉酱"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ranch dressing', 'str_pl': 'ranch dressing'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Ranch dressing, great on salad or with chicken strips, fries, and burgers. "
"This is a commercial version loaded with artificial preservatives for longer"
" shelf life."
msgstr "牧场沙拉酱，配沙拉、鸡柳、薯条和汉堡都很棒。这是为延长保质期而添加了大量人工防腐剂的商业版本。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "teriyaki sauce"
msgid_plural "teriyaki sauce"
msgstr[0] "照烧酱"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'teriyaki sauce', 'str_pl': 'teriyaki sauce'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Teriyaki sauce. It goes well with chow mein, stir fry, or on chicken and "
"burgers."
msgstr "照烧酱。它非常适合搭配炒面、炒菜，或者涂在鸡肉和汉堡上。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "hot pepper sauce"
msgid_plural "hot pepper sauce"
msgstr[0] "辣椒酱"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hot pepper sauce', 'str_pl': 'hot pepper sauce'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"The red rooster! Good on just about anything savory. Not a good idea to "
"drink it!"
msgstr "红公鸡辣椒酱！几乎配任何咸味食物都很棒。但直接喝可不是个好主意！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "cocoa powder"
msgid_plural "cocoa powder"
msgstr[0] "可可粉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cocoa powder', 'str_pl': 'cocoa powder'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A large tub of mild chocolate in powdered form. Intended for baking, not "
"mixing, but would do in a pinch for an emergency refreshment."
msgstr "一大罐温和的巧克力粉末。本用于烘焙而非冲泡，但在紧急情况下也可用来制作临时饮品。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "chocolate drink mix"
msgid_plural "chocolate drink mixes"
msgstr[0] "巧克力饮料粉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'chocolate drink mix', 'str_pl': 'chocolate drink
#. mixes'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A large tub of commercial chocolate milk mix. Not recommended dry, but "
"amazing when mixed!"
msgstr "一大罐商业巧克力牛奶粉。不建议干吃，但冲泡后味道超棒！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "fruit punch mix"
msgid_plural "fruit punch mixes"
msgstr[0] "水果潘趣饮料粉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fruit punch mix', 'str_pl': 'fruit punch mixes'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Fruit punch powder! OH YEAAAAAAAH! Not recommended dry!"
msgstr "水果潘趣粉！哦耶——！不建议干吃！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "orange drink mix"
msgid_plural "orange drink mixes"
msgstr[0] "橙味饮料粉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'orange drink mix', 'str_pl': 'orange drink
#. mixes'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Tangy, unusually sweet orange drink mix! Not recommended dry!"
msgstr "酸爽、异常甜美的橙味饮料粉！不建议干吃！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "grape drink mix"
msgid_plural "grape drink mixes"
msgstr[0] "葡萄味饮料粉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'grape drink mix', 'str_pl': 'grape drink mixes'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Particularly sweet grape drink powder! Don't ya wanna? Not recommended dry!"
msgstr "特别甜的葡萄味饮料粉！不想来点吗？不建议干吃！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "root beer drink mix"
msgid_plural "root beer drink mixes"
msgstr[0] "根汁汽水饮料粉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'root beer drink mix', 'str_pl': 'root beer drink
#. mixes'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Complicated. Multifaceted. Root beer! In powder form."
msgstr "复杂。多层次。根汁汽水！粉状形态。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "orange drink (mixed)"
msgid_plural "orange drinks (mixed)"
msgstr[0] "橙味饮料（已调配）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'orange drink (mixed)', 'str_pl': 'orange drinks
#. (mixed)'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Orange drink from powder. Much better mixed!"
msgstr "由粉末调制的橙味饮料。调配后风味更佳！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "fruit punch drink (mixed)"
msgid_plural "fruit punch drinks (mixed)"
msgstr[0] "水果宾治饮料（已调配）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fruit punch drink (mixed)', 'str_pl': 'fruit
#. punch drinks (mixed)'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "The fruit punch most kids grew up with. OH YEAAAAAAAH!"
msgstr "大多数孩子童年记忆中的水果宾治。哦耶————！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "grape drink (mixed)"
msgid_plural "grape drinks (mixed)"
msgstr[0] "葡萄味饮料（已调配）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'grape drink (mixed)', 'str_pl': 'grape drinks
#. (mixed)'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Better now that it's mixed, this grape drink will take you way back. Don't "
"you wanna?"
msgstr "调配后风味更佳，这款葡萄饮料将带你重回旧日时光。不想试试吗？"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "root beer drink (mixed)"
msgid_plural "root beer drinks (mixed)"
msgstr[0] "根汁汽水饮料（已调配）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'root beer drink (mixed)', 'str_pl': 'root beer
#. drinks (mixed)'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"One of the most complicated flavor mixes of all time, this is root beer, "
"straight from powder. Delicious!"
msgstr "史上最复杂的风味调配之一，这是直接用粉末冲调的根汁汽水。美味！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "chocolate drink (mixed)"
msgid_plural "chocolate drinks (mixed)"
msgstr[0] "巧克力饮料（已调配）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'chocolate drink (mixed)', 'str_pl': 'chocolate
#. drinks (mixed)'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"No longer solely the drink of the gods, now you too can feel elevated with "
"some cocoa-powered sweetness!"
msgstr "不再是神明专属饮品，现在你也能通过可可带来的甜蜜感受升华！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "cocoa drink"
msgid_plural "cocoa drink"
msgstr[0] "可可饮料"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cocoa drink', 'str_pl': 'cocoa drink'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"This is chocolate milk made using baker's chocolate powder. It is bitter and"
" milder than purpose-built drink mix, but still chocolatey enough to enjoy. "
"Sort of."
msgstr "这是用烘焙可可粉调制的巧克力牛奶。比专用冲调饮料更苦涩清淡，但仍保有足够巧克力风味以供享用。大概吧。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "orange juice"
msgid_plural "orange juices"
msgstr[0] "橙汁"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'orange juice'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Mass-produced national brand orange juice, loaded with artificial flavoring "
"and preservatives. This is pulp-free and has a much sweeter less citrus "
"flavor thanks to the added sugar. Completely devoid of health benefits!"
msgstr "量产国民品牌橙汁，富含人工香精与防腐剂。无果肉，因添加糖分而更甜且柑橘风味减弱。完全无健康益处！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "apple juice"
msgid_plural "apple juices"
msgstr[0] "苹果汁"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'apple juice'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Mass-produced national brand apple juice, loaded with artificial flavoring "
"and preservatives. Much more pronounced sweet flavor thanks to the added "
"sugar. Completely devoid of health benefits!"
msgstr "量产国民品牌苹果汁，富含人工香精与防腐剂。因添加糖分而甜味更突出。完全无健康益处！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "cranberry juice"
msgid_plural "cranberry juices"
msgstr[0] "蔓越莓汁"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cranberry juice'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Mass-produced national brand cranberry juice, loaded with artificial "
"flavoring and preservatives. Much more tolerable than fresh juice thanks to "
"the added sweeteners. Completely devoid of health benefits!"
msgstr "量产国民品牌蔓越莓汁，富含人工香精与防腐剂。因添加甜味剂比鲜榨果汁更易入口。完全无健康益处！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "grape juice"
msgid_plural "grape juices"
msgstr[0] "葡萄汁"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'grape juice'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Mass-produced national brand grape juice, loaded with artificial flavoring "
"and preservatives. Tastes nothing like real grapes but in this case that's "
"not a bad thing. Completely devoid of health benefits!"
msgstr "量产国民品牌葡萄汁，富含人工香精与防腐剂。毫无真实葡萄风味，但在此情况下并非坏事。完全无健康益处！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "pineapple juice"
msgid_plural "pineapple juices"
msgstr[0] "菠萝汁"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pineapple juice'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Mass-produced national brand pineapple juice. The flavor is obviously "
"artificial, like most of the ingredients, but it still carries the sweetness"
" of its host fruit. This is loaded to the gills with artificial "
"preservatives and coloring to keep it shelf-stable and appealing."
msgstr "量产国民品牌菠萝汁。风味明显人工化，如同大部分成分，但仍保留原果甜味。为保持货架稳定与诱人外观，添加了大量人工防腐剂与色素。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'grape juice'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Slightly sweetened all-natural concord grape juice, freshly pressed! "
"Delicious and healthy."
msgstr "轻微加糖的全天然康科德葡萄汁，新鲜压榨！美味又健康。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pineapple juice'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"The sweetest natural juice you can find: fresh pressed pineapple! And "
"healthy for you, to boot!"
msgstr "你能找到的最甜天然果汁：新鲜压榨菠萝汁！而且还很健康！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "sports drink"
msgid_plural "sports drinks"
msgstr[0] "运动饮料"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sports drink'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Electrolytes. Sugar. Artificial fruit punch flavoring. High profile "
"labeling. Designed for marathon runners and olympians. Even though the "
"flavor is subdued, it's not bad tasting. But it would be better chilled."
msgstr "电解质。糖分。人工水果宾治香精。醒目标签。专为马拉松跑者与奥运选手设计。尽管风味清淡，但口感不差。冰镇后会更佳。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "condensed milk"
msgid_plural "condensed milk"
msgstr[0] "炼乳"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'condensed milk', 'str_pl': 'condensed milk'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Baby cow food, appropriated for adult humans.  Having been canned, this milk"
" should last for a very long time."
msgstr "幼牛食物，被人类成人征用。经罐装处理后，此牛奶可保存极长时间。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "V8"
msgid_plural "V8s"
msgstr[0] "V8果蔬汁"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'V8'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Commercial big-brand healthy drink! Has artificial preservatives and 20% "
"juice! Contains up to eight vegetable flavors!! Tasty and nutritious but not"
" as healthy as fresh juiced veggies!"
msgstr "商业大牌健康饮品！含人工防腐剂与20%果汁！最多包含八种蔬菜风味！！美味又营养，但不如新鲜榨取的蔬菜汁健康！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "cheesecake wheel"
msgid_plural "cheesecake wheels"
msgstr[0] "芝士蛋糕轮"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cheesecake wheel'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A whole wheel of New York style cheesecake! Still in its original packaging."
" What a score!"
msgstr "一整轮纽约风格芝士蛋糕！仍保留原始包装。真是好收获！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cheesecake wheel'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A whole wheel of marbled chocolate cheesecake! Still in its original "
"packaging. What a score!"
msgstr "一整轮大理石纹巧克力芝士蛋糕！仍保留原始包装。真是好收获！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cheesecake wheel'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A whole wheel of variety sampler cheesecake! Still in its original "
"packaging. What a score!"
msgstr "一整轮多样品尝装芝士蛋糕！仍保留原始包装。真是好收获！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "cake"
msgid_plural "cakes"
msgstr[0] "蛋糕"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cake'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Red velvet cake! Smooth and luscious."
msgstr "红丝绒蛋糕！柔滑诱人。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cake'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Carrot cake! Crumbly."
msgstr "胡萝卜蛋糕！酥脆易碎。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cake'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A pumpkin spice cake!"
msgstr "南瓜香料蛋糕！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cake'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "German chocolate cake! What a rare treat!"
msgstr "德国巧克力蛋糕！真是难得的享受！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cake'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"The cake is topped with edible paper depicting a scene of four young-looking"
" girls with oddly-colored hair raising their arms in cheer. For some reason "
"there are bumps in the cake where the breasts are. It makes you wonder what "
"kind of person originally ordered this made."
msgstr ""
"蛋糕顶部装饰着可食用纸，描绘了四名发色奇异的年轻女孩举臂欢呼的场景。不知为何，蛋糕在胸部位置有凸起。这让你不禁好奇最初定制这款蛋糕的是怎样的人。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "party platter"
msgid_plural "party platters"
msgstr[0] "派对拼盘"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'party platter'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A sampler tray of 4 different kinds of sliced cheeses."
msgstr "装有4种不同切片奶酪的品尝盘。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'party platter'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A sampler tray of 4 different kinds of sliced meats."
msgstr "装有4种不同切片肉类的品尝盘。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'party platter'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A tray of pre-cooked unbreaded shrimp with a tartar sauce cup in the middle."
msgstr "一盘预煮的无面包屑虾，中间配有一杯塔塔酱。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'party platter'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A variety tray of 3 different kinds of crackers, 2 kinds of cheese, and thin"
" summer sausage slices."
msgstr "多样拼盘，包含3种不同饼干、2种奶酪和薄切夏令香肠片。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "submarine sandwich"
msgid_plural "submarine sandwiches"
msgstr[0] "潜艇三明治"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'submarine sandwich', 'str_pl': 'submarine
#. sandwiches'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A freshly prepared footlong sandwich composed of 3 different sliced meats, 2"
" different sliced cheeses, tomatoes, lettuce, onions, and a liberal smear of"
" proprietary dressing topped off with oil."
msgstr "新鲜制作的一英尺长三明治，包含3种不同切片肉类、2种不同切片奶酪、番茄、生菜、洋葱，并慷慨涂抹了特制酱料，最后淋上油。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'submarine sandwich', 'str_pl': 'submarine
#. sandwiches'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A freshly prepared footlong veggie supreme. Has tomatoes, two different "
"types of lettuce, both green and white onions, cucumbers, banana peppers, "
"jalapenos, and olives drenched in a flavored olive oil dressing."
msgstr "新鲜制作的一英尺长蔬菜至尊三明治。包含番茄、两种不同生菜、青葱与白洋葱、黄瓜、香蕉椒、墨西哥辣椒和橄榄，浸泡在风味橄榄油酱汁中。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "panini"
msgid_plural "paninis"
msgstr[0] "帕尼尼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'panini'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A philly cheesesteak panini."
msgstr "费城芝士牛排帕尼尼。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'panini'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A grilled chicken cheese panini."
msgstr "烤鸡芝士帕尼尼。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "lunch wrap"
msgid_plural "lunch wraps"
msgstr[0] "午餐卷饼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'lunch wrap'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"This is a chicken BLT ranch wrap. It takes you back to better times, when "
"things were simpler. When the deli was running you'd get these in halves, "
"but looks like you get a whole wrap this time!"
msgstr "这是鸡肉培根生菜牧场酱卷饼。它将你带回更美好的时光，那时一切更简单。熟食店营业时你只能买到半份，但这次看来你能得到一整份卷饼！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'lunch wrap'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"This is a tofu and veggie wrap. Not nearly as satisfying as a chicken wrap, "
"but four time as good for you! When the deli was running you'd get these in "
"halves, but looks like you get a whole wrap this time!"
msgstr "这是豆腐蔬菜卷饼。虽不如鸡肉卷饼满足，但对健康的好处却是四倍！熟食店营业时你只能买到半份，但这次看来你能得到一整份卷饼！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "potato wedges"
msgid_plural "potato wedges"
msgstr[0] "薯角"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'potato wedges', 'str_pl': 'potato wedges'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Fried to golden brown perfection, these salty slices are guaranteed to "
"please. Will make you thirsty!"
msgstr "炸至金黄完美，这些咸香薯片保证令人满意。会让你口渴！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "steak fries"
msgid_plural "steak fries"
msgstr[0] "牛排薯条"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'steak fries', 'str_pl': 'steak fries'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Thick cut potato slices, fried to a golden greasy brown and generously "
"salted. The perfect modern complement to a burger."
msgstr "厚切土豆片，炸至金黄油腻的棕色，并慷慨撒盐。是现代汉堡的完美搭配。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "curly fries"
msgid_plural "curly fries"
msgstr[0] "卷卷薯条"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'curly fries', 'str_pl': 'curly fries'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Long spirals of delightfully salty, greasy potatoes."
msgstr "长长的螺旋状土豆条，咸香可口，油脂丰富。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "deli corn dogs"
msgid_plural "deli corn dogs"
msgstr[0] "熟食玉米热狗"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'deli corn dogs', 'str_pl': 'deli corn dogs'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"These are corn dogs the way they were meant to be eaten - greasy, fatty, and"
" full of flavor straight from a commercial deep fryer. Frozen corn dogs just"
" simply can't compare."
msgstr "这才是玉米热狗应有的吃法——油腻、肥美、风味十足，直接从商用油炸锅中取出。冷冻玉米热狗根本无法与之相比。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "burritos"
msgid_plural "burritos"
msgstr[0] "墨西哥卷饼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'burritos', 'str_pl': 'burritos'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A pair of soft-shell burritos filled with gooey beans and cheese."
msgstr "一对软皮墨西哥卷饼，内馅是黏稠的豆泥和奶酪。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'burritos', 'str_pl': 'burritos'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A pair of soft-shell burritos filled with the works. Succulent meat. Crisp "
"veggies. Gooey cheese. Heaping tablespoons of sour cream and guacamole."
msgstr "一对软皮墨西哥卷饼，馅料丰富。多汁的肉、爽脆的蔬菜、黏稠的奶酪，还有堆成小山般的酸奶油和鳄梨酱。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "mozzarella sticks"
msgid_plural "mozzarella sticks"
msgstr[0] "马苏里拉奶酪条"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mozzarella sticks', 'str_pl': 'mozzarella
#. sticks'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A handful of mozzarella sticks. Gooey. Golden brown. Greasy. So worth it."
msgstr "一把马苏里拉奶酪条。黏稠、金黄、油腻，但绝对值得。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "chicken fries"
msgid_plural "chicken fries"
msgstr[0] "鸡肉薯条"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'chicken fries', 'str_pl': 'chicken fries'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A handful of chicken sticks. The convenience of minced meat, in the "
"convenient form of fries!"
msgstr "一把鸡肉条。碎肉的便利，薯条的形态！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "stuffed pepper"
msgid_plural "stuffed peppers"
msgstr[0] "酿甜椒"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'stuffed pepper'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A large bell pepper, cored and stuffed with rice, beef, tomatoes, corn, and "
"melted colbyjack cheese."
msgstr "一个大甜椒，去核后填入米饭、牛肉、番茄、玉米和融化的科尔比杰克奶酪。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "poutine"
msgid_plural "poutine"
msgstr[0] "肉汁奶酪薯条"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'poutine', 'str_pl': 'poutine'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A specialty from New England's northern neighbors, this is fries drenched in"
" a meat gravy and liberally covered with fried cheese curds."
msgstr "这道新英格兰北部邻国的特色菜，是将薯条浸在肉汁中，并慷慨地撒上油炸奶酪凝块。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "tortilla chips and salsa"
msgid_plural "tortilla chips and salsa"
msgstr[0] "玉米片和莎莎酱"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tortilla chips and salsa', 'str_pl': 'tortilla
#. chips and salsa'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Some corn chips with a side of habanero salsa."
msgstr "一些玉米片，配上一小份哈瓦那辣椒莎莎酱。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "meatloaf"
msgid_plural "meatloaf"
msgstr[0] "肉饼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'meatloaf', 'str_pl': 'meatloaf'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Ground meat formed into a well-browned loaf in a thick gravy slathered with "
"smoky barbeque sauce."
msgstr "碎肉制成烤得焦黄的面包状，淋上浓稠的肉汁，再涂满烟熏烧烤酱。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "stuffed mushroom"
msgid_plural "stuffed mushrooms"
msgstr[0] "酿蘑菇"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'stuffed mushroom', 'str_pl': 'stuffed
#. mushrooms'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Succulent portabello mushrooms hollowed out and filled with rice, melted "
"cheese, deeply browned ground meat, and roasted veggies."
msgstr "多汁的波特贝洛蘑菇，挖空后填入米饭、融化的奶酪、深褐色的碎肉和烤蔬菜。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "potato salad"
msgid_plural "potato salads"
msgstr[0] "土豆沙拉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'potato salad', 'str_pl': 'potato salads'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Classic potato salad. Filling, but mildly thirst-provoking."
msgstr "经典土豆沙拉。饱腹，但会微微引发口渴。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "german potato salad"
msgid_plural "german potato salads"
msgstr[0] "德式土豆沙拉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'german potato salad', 'str_pl': 'german potato
#. salads'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"German potato salad. With the addition of diced pickles, mustard, and thick "
"smoky bacon, it's much heartier and more savory than classic potato salad."
msgstr "德式土豆沙拉。加入了切碎的腌黄瓜、芥末和厚实的烟熏培根，比经典土豆沙拉更丰盛、更美味。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "mashed potatoes"
msgid_plural "mashed potatoes"
msgstr[0] "土豆泥"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mashed potatoes', 'str_pl': 'mashed potatoes'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Mashed potatoes with a light dusting of salt, pepper, and mild spice. Served"
" with brown gravy."
msgstr "土豆泥，轻轻撒上盐、胡椒和温和的香料。配以棕色肉汁。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "macaroni salad"
msgid_plural "macaroni salads"
msgstr[0] "通心粉沙拉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'macaroni salad', 'str_pl': 'macaroni salads'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Classic macaroni salad. Refreshing."
msgstr "经典通心粉沙拉。清爽可口。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "seafood salad"
msgid_plural "seafood salads"
msgstr[0] "海鲜沙拉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'seafood salad', 'str_pl': 'seafood salads'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A New England variation on the traditional tuna salad, this one instead "
"features hake, cod, lobster, and crab, all minced with a light savory cream "
"and robust spice blend."
msgstr "这是新英格兰对传统金枪鱼沙拉的改良版，以鳕鱼、鳕鱼、龙虾和蟹肉为特色，全部切碎后拌入清淡的咸味奶油和浓郁的香料混合物中。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "fruit salad"
msgid_plural "fruit salads"
msgstr[0] "水果沙拉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fruit salad', 'str_pl': 'fruit salads'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Sweetened fruit chunks in a mix of their own syrup and vanilla-flavored "
"heavy whipping cream dusted with cinnamon. Mildly good for you!"
msgstr "甜味水果块混合在自制的糖浆和香草风味重奶油中，撒上肉桂粉。对健康略有裨益！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "casserole"
msgid_plural "casseroles"
msgstr[0] "砂锅菜"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'casserole', 'str_pl': 'casseroles'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"This is a breakfast casserole, a combination of eggs, milk, tater tots, "
"bacon, and spices all baked together to a uniform golden brown."
msgstr "这是一道早餐砂锅菜，将鸡蛋、牛奶、土豆饼、培根和香料混合在一起，烘烤至均匀的金黄色。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'casserole', 'str_pl': 'casseroles'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"This is a broccoli bake casserole, a combination of broccoli florets in "
"mayonnaise and cream of chicken with herbs, topped generously with thick "
"layers of cheese, and then baked to golden brown. Healthy, fattening, and "
"delicious."
msgstr "这是一道西兰花烤砂锅菜，将西兰花小花拌入蛋黄酱和鸡肉奶油汤中，加入香草，顶部慷慨地覆盖厚厚的奶酪层，然后烘烤至金黄色。健康、增肥且美味。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'casserole', 'str_pl': 'casseroles'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "This is a tuna casserole."
msgstr "这是一道金枪鱼砂锅菜。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "schnitzel"
msgid_plural "schnitzel"
msgstr[0] "炸肉排"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'schnitzel', 'str_pl': 'schnitzel'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A breaded cutlet of meat, prepared German-style."
msgstr "一块裹面包屑的肉排，以德式风格烹制。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "saurbraten"
msgid_plural "saurbraten"
msgstr[0] "酸炖牛肉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'saurbraten', 'str_pl': 'saurbraten'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A German hallmark, this is a soft, juicy, tender roast of meat with various "
"herbs, seasoings, and spices. Has a sour kick to it due to having marinated "
"in vinegar and red wine for days before roasting."
msgstr "这是德国的标志性菜肴，一种柔软、多汁、嫩滑的烤肉，配以各种香草、调味料和香料。由于在烘烤前用醋和红酒腌制数日，带有酸味刺激。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "german potato pancakes"
msgid_plural "german potato pancakes"
msgstr[0] "德式土豆煎饼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'german potato pancakes', 'str_pl': 'german
#. potato pancakes'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Pancakes from ground potatoes, egg, and flour. Having a neutral flavor by "
"themselves, they go well with either savory or sweet toppings. These ones "
"have apple sauce and sugar liberally drizzled over them."
msgstr "由磨碎的土豆、鸡蛋和面粉制成的煎饼。本身味道中性，适合搭配咸味或甜味配料。这些煎饼上淋有大量的苹果酱和糖。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'german potato pancakes', 'str_pl': 'german
#. potato pancakes'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Pancakes from ground potatoes, egg, and flour. Having a neutral flavor by "
"themselves, they go well with either savory or sweet toppings. These ones "
"have cottage cheese and sour cream spread over them."
msgstr "由磨碎的土豆、鸡蛋和面粉制成的煎饼。本身味道中性，适合搭配咸味或甜味配料。这些煎饼上涂有农家干酪和酸奶油。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "speckkuchen"
msgid_plural "speckkuchen"
msgstr[0] "培根蛋糕"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'speckkuchen', 'str_pl': 'speckkuchen'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A German take on quiche, this one uses rye instead of traditional wheat "
"flour for the base, and features bacon crumbles covering the top."
msgstr "这是德国风味的乳蛋饼，使用黑麦而非传统小麦粉作为基底，顶部覆盖培根碎。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "pizza sticks"
msgid_plural "pizza sticks"
msgstr[0] "披萨棒"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pizza sticks', 'str_pl': 'pizza sticks'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Pizza in the convenience of a slimmed down hot pocket. Pepperoni and sausage"
" in piping hot, gooey mozzarella and marinara."
msgstr "披萨以简化版热口袋的形式呈现，方便食用。内含意大利辣香肠和香肠，搭配滚烫、粘稠的马苏里拉奶酪和意式番茄酱。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "hot pocket"
msgid_plural "hot pockets"
msgstr[0] "热口袋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hot pocket', 'str_pl': 'hot pockets'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A hot pocket! This one is meatball marinara with melted mozzarella."
msgstr "一个热口袋！这个是肉丸意式番茄酱口味，搭配融化的马苏里拉奶酪。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hot pocket', 'str_pl': 'hot pockets'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A hot pocket! This one is ham and cheese."
msgstr "一个热口袋！这个是火腿奶酪口味。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hot pocket', 'str_pl': 'hot pockets'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A hot pocket! This one is pepperoni pizza."
msgstr "一个热口袋！这个是意大利辣香肠披萨口味。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hot pocket', 'str_pl': 'hot pockets'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A hot pocket! This one is philly cheesesteak."
msgstr "一个热口袋！这个是费城芝士牛排口味。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "borscht"
msgid_plural "borscht"
msgstr[0] "罗宋汤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'borscht', 'str_pl': 'borscht'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A very sour beet root soup with beef stock and assorted sauteed veggies. "
"Good for you, but not particularly palatable."
msgstr "一种非常酸的甜菜根汤，加入牛肉高汤和各种炒蔬菜。对健康有益，但口感不佳。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "carbonara"
msgid_plural "carbonara"
msgstr[0] "卡邦尼意面"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'carbonara', 'str_pl': 'carbonara'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Goopy carbonara! Wavy al dente egg noodles in a thick sauce of egg, heavy "
"cream, and parmesan finished with minced garlic, onion, and thick-cut bacon "
"chopped into chunks. The deli version has a proprietary blend of spices and "
"seasoning that significantly heighten the overall flavor profile."
msgstr ""
"粘稠的卡邦尼意面！波浪状的弹牙鸡蛋面裹在由鸡蛋、重奶油和帕尔马干酪制成的浓稠酱汁中，最后加入蒜末、洋葱和切块的厚切培根。熟食店版本采用独家混合香料和调味料，显著提升了整体风味。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "cheese wheel"
msgid_plural "cheese wheels"
msgstr[0] "奶酪轮"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cheese wheel'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A wheel of soft cheddar cheese."
msgstr "一个软质切达奶酪轮。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cheese wheel'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A wheel of hard, tart cheddar cheese."
msgstr "一个硬质、酸味的切达奶酪轮。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cheese wheel'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A wheel of smooth muenster cheese."
msgstr "一个光滑的明斯特奶酪轮。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cheese wheel'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A wheel of slightly aromatic swiss cheese."
msgstr "一块略带香气的瑞士奶酪轮。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cheese wheel'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A wheel of moist, delicate colbyjack cheese."
msgstr "一块湿润、细腻的科尔比杰克奶酪轮。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cheese wheel'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A wheel of firm, crumbly parmesan cheese."
msgstr "一块坚硬、易碎的帕尔马干酪轮。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cheese wheel'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A wheel of creamy gouda cheese."
msgstr "一块奶油质地的豪达奶酪轮。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "cottage cheese"
msgid_plural "cottage cheeses"
msgstr[0] "乡村奶酪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cottage cheese'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A two pound container of whole fat large-curd cottage cheese with high "
"moisture content. Good on its own, or as a side dish to virtually anything. "
"Especially good in lasagna!"
msgstr "一罐两磅重、高水分含量的全脂大凝乳乡村奶酪。单吃不错，或作为几乎所有菜肴的配菜。尤其适合用于千层面！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "cream cheese"
msgid_plural "cream cheeses"
msgstr[0] "奶油奶酪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cream cheese'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A two pound container of whole fat cream cheese. Slightly tart and dry by "
"itself, but good for baking with."
msgstr "一罐两磅重的全脂奶油奶酪。单吃略带酸味和干涩，但适合用于烘焙。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "ricotta cheese"
msgid_plural "ricotta cheeses"
msgstr[0] "里科塔奶酪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ricotta cheese'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A two pound container of whole fat ricotta cheese. Slightly sweeter than "
"cottage cheese and with about the same moisture content. Great for "
"garnishing pastas in general."
msgstr "一罐两磅重的全脂里科塔奶酪。比乡村奶酪稍甜，水分含量相近。非常适合用于装饰各种意面。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "sliced meat"
msgid_plural "sliced meats"
msgstr[0] "切片肉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sliced meat'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "About a pound of deli-sliced meat. This is mesquite turkey."
msgstr "大约一磅熟食店切片肉。这是豆科灌木火鸡肉。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sliced meat'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "About a pound of deli-sliced meat. This is honey-glazed turkey."
msgstr "大约一磅熟食店切片肉。这是蜂蜜釉火鸡肉。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sliced meat'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "About a pound of deli-sliced meat. This is smoked ham."
msgstr "大约一磅熟食店切片肉。这是烟熏火腿。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sliced meat'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "About a pound of deli-sliced meat. This is honey-baked ham."
msgstr "大约一磅熟食店切片肉。这是蜂蜜烤火腿。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sliced meat'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "About a pound of deli-sliced meat. This is roasted chicken."
msgstr "大约一磅熟食店切片肉。这是烤鸡肉。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sliced meat'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "About a pound of deli-sliced meat. This is pepper chicken."
msgstr "大约一磅熟食店切片肉。这是胡椒鸡肉。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sliced meat'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "About a pound of deli-sliced meat. This is roast beef."
msgstr "大约一磅熟食店切片肉。这是烤牛肉。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "steak"
msgid_plural "steaks"
msgstr[0] "牛排"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'steak', 'str_pl': 'steaks'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A fully cooked slab of beef. This is a t-bone."
msgstr "一块完全烹熟的牛肉块。这是T骨牛排。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'steak', 'str_pl': 'steaks'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A fully cooked slab of beef. This is a ribeye."
msgstr "一块完全烹熟的牛肉块。这是肋眼牛排。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'steak', 'str_pl': 'steaks'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A fully cooked slab of beef. This is a sirloin."
msgstr "一块完全烹熟的牛肉块。这是西冷牛排。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'steak', 'str_pl': 'steaks'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A fully cooked slab of beef. This is a tri-tip."
msgstr "一块完全烹熟的牛肉块。这是三角牛排。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "roasted chicken"
msgid_plural "roasted chickens"
msgstr[0] "烤鸡"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'roasted chicken'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A whole bone-in chicken, roasted rotisserie-style. Juicy and filling."
msgstr "一整只带骨鸡肉，以旋转烤架风格烤制。多汁且饱腹。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "deli chicken"
msgid_plural "deli chicken"
msgstr[0] "熟食鸡肉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'deli chicken', 'str_pl': 'deli chicken'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A generous assortment of breaded boneless wings, thighs, and breasts. This "
"is the teriyaki glaze."
msgstr "一份丰盛的面包屑无骨鸡翅、鸡腿和鸡胸肉组合。这是照烧酱口味。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'deli chicken', 'str_pl': 'deli chicken'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A generous assortment of breaded boneless wings, thighs, and breasts. This "
"is the bourbon barbeque glaze."
msgstr "一份丰盛的面包屑无骨鸡翅、鸡腿和鸡胸肉组合。这是波本烧烤酱口味。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'deli chicken', 'str_pl': 'deli chicken'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A generous assortment of breaded boneless wings, thighs, and breasts. This "
"is the orange chicken glaze."
msgstr "一份丰盛的面包屑无骨鸡翅、鸡腿和鸡胸肉组合。这是橙子鸡酱口味。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'deli chicken', 'str_pl': 'deli chicken'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A generous assortment of breaded boneless wings, thighs, and breasts. This "
"is the spicy general tso glaze with whole chili pods."
msgstr "一份丰盛的面包屑无骨鸡翅、鸡腿和鸡胸肉组合。这是辣味左宗棠酱口味，带有整颗辣椒荚。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "fried chicken"
msgid_plural "fried chicken"
msgstr[0] "炸鸡"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fried chicken', 'str_pl': 'fried chicken'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Deep fried breaded bone-in chicken wings, thighs, and breasts. Mild "
"seasoning blend."
msgstr "油炸裹粉的带骨鸡翅、鸡腿和鸡胸肉。采用温和调味料混合。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fried chicken', 'str_pl': 'fried chicken'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Deep fried breaded bone-in chicken wings, thighs, and breasts. Spicy "
"seasoning blend."
msgstr "油炸裹粉的带骨鸡翅、鸡腿和鸡胸肉。采用辛辣调味料混合。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fried chicken', 'str_pl': 'fried chicken'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Deep fried breaded bone-in chicken wings, thighs, and breasts. Barbeque "
"glaze."
msgstr "油炸裹粉的带骨鸡翅、鸡腿和鸡胸肉。涂有烧烤酱汁。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fried chicken', 'str_pl': 'fried chicken'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Deep fried breaded bone-in chicken wings, thighs, and breasts. Habanero "
"glaze."
msgstr "油炸裹粉的带骨鸡翅、鸡腿和鸡胸肉。涂有哈瓦那辣椒酱汁。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "crab cake"
msgid_plural "crab cakes"
msgstr[0] "蟹肉饼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'crab cake', 'str_pl': 'crab cakes'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"An iconic nationwide dish, this is a golden brown breaded ball of minced "
"crab meat and finely diced savory vegetables with a signature new england "
"herb blend."
msgstr "这是一道全国闻名的标志性菜肴，由蟹肉末和精细切丁的香草蔬菜混合而成，裹上面包屑炸至金黄，并配有新英格兰特色香草混合料。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "new england cod fish cake"
msgid_plural "new england cod fish cakes"
msgstr[0] "新英格兰鳕鱼饼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'new england cod fish cake', 'str_pl': 'new
#. england cod fish cakes'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A deep browned formed cake of minced cod fish meat, potato, onion, and herbs"
" with an incredibly savory flavor. Served with tartar sauce. A regional "
"specialty."
msgstr "由鳕鱼肉末、土豆、洋葱和香草混合制成的深褐色成型饼，风味极其鲜美。搭配塔塔酱食用。一道地方特色菜。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "grilled calamari"
msgid_plural "grilled calamari"
msgstr[0] "烤鱿鱼圈"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'grilled calamari', 'str_pl': 'grilled calamari'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Several rings of squid meat grilled until thick and firm with a light sear."
msgstr "几圈鱿鱼肉烤至厚实紧致，表面微焦。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "coastal seafood cup"
msgid_plural "coastal seafood cups"
msgstr[0] "海岸海鲜杯"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'coastal seafood cup', 'str_pl': 'coastal seafood
#. cups'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A hollowed out cucumber 'cup' containing a blend of plain yogurt, hot sauce,"
" and dijon mustard, with a combination of minced crabmeat and minced lobster"
" folded in and topped with black peppercorns."
msgstr "一个挖空的黄瓜“杯”，内盛原味酸奶、辣酱和第戎芥末的混合酱汁，拌入蟹肉末和龙虾肉末，顶部撒上黑胡椒粒。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "lobster thermidor roll"
msgid_plural "lobster thermidor rolls"
msgstr[0] "龙虾瑟米多卷"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'lobster thermidor roll', 'str_pl': 'lobster
#. thermidor rolls'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Creamy, cheesy lobster resting on a bed of fresh shredded lettuce in a whole"
" wheat roll and drizzled with zesty lemon-flavored yogurt dressing. A "
"traditional recipe, made portable!"
msgstr "奶油芝士龙虾肉铺在新鲜切碎的生菜上，夹在全麦卷中，淋上清爽的柠檬风味酸奶酱。传统食谱，便携享用！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "fried belly clams"
msgid_plural "fried belly clams"
msgstr[0] "炸蛤蜊肚"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fried belly clams', 'str_pl': 'fried belly
#. clams'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Basically clam strips, but thicker and more flavorful with the same "
"delicious deep fried breading."
msgstr "本质上是蛤蜊条，但更厚实、风味更浓郁，裹着同样美味的油炸面包屑。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "fried scallops"
msgid_plural "fried scallops"
msgstr[0] "炸扇贝"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fried scallops', 'str_pl': 'fried scallops'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Deep-fried golden-brown nuggets filled with flaky fish. The perfect side "
"dish to any proper New England meal."
msgstr "油炸至金黄色的块状物，内填片状鱼肉。任何正宗新英格兰餐点的完美配菜。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "salmon cakes"
msgid_plural "salmon cakes"
msgstr[0] "三文鱼饼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'salmon cakes', 'str_pl': 'salmon cakes'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Minced salmon with a light breading shaped into a large, light patty and "
"thoroughly browned. The northeasterner's answer to the meatloaf."
msgstr "三文鱼末裹上轻薄面包屑，塑形成大而轻盈的肉饼，彻底煎至褐色。这是东北地区对肉糕的回应。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "broiled swordfish kebabs"
msgid_plural "broiled swordfish kebabs"
msgstr[0] "烤剑鱼串"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broiled swordfish kebabs', 'str_pl': 'broiled
#. swordfish kebabs'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Short of whale or shark meat, this is the heartiest meat in the sea. "
"Broiled, it's got an out-of-this-world umami profile that's well-"
"complemented by the interspersed vegetable rounds."
msgstr "除了鲸鱼肉或鲨鱼肉，这是海洋中最丰盛的肉类。烤制后，它带有超凡的鲜味，与穿插其间的蔬菜片相得益彰。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "lobster mac and cheese"
msgid_plural "lobster mac and cheese"
msgstr[0] "龙虾通心粉和奶酪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'lobster mac and cheese', 'str_pl': 'lobster mac
#. and cheese'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Bite-sized cooked-through lobster bits in three different varieties of gooey"
" cheese with diced onion, minced garlic, and buttery pasta. An American "
"classic, Yankee style."
msgstr "一口大小的熟龙虾块，搭配三种不同口感的粘稠奶酪，以及洋葱丁、蒜末和黄油意面。一道美国经典，扬基风格。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "chow mein"
msgid_plural "chow mein"
msgstr[0] "炒面"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'chow mein', 'str_pl': 'chow mein'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Oily stirfried noodles with veggies and meat."
msgstr "油炒面条，配以蔬菜和肉类。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "potstickers"
msgid_plural "potstickers"
msgstr[0] "锅贴"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'potstickers', 'str_pl': 'potstickers'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Fried stuffed dumplings with cabbage and pork."
msgstr "油炸馅料饺子，内含卷心菜和猪肉。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "wontons"
msgid_plural "wontons"
msgstr[0] "馄饨"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wontons', 'str_pl': 'wontons'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Crispy dumplings filled with cabbage and pork."
msgstr "酥脆的饺子，内馅为白菜猪肉。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wontons', 'str_pl': 'wontons'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Crispy dumplings filled with cream cheese and imitation crab meat."
msgstr "酥脆的饺子，内馅为奶油芝士和仿蟹肉。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "mongolian beef"
msgid_plural "mongolian beef"
msgstr[0] "蒙古牛肉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mongolian beef', 'str_pl': 'mongolian beef'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Thin oily slices of beef on a bed of sticky white rice with a savory sauce."
msgstr "薄而油润的牛肉片铺在黏糯的白米饭上，佐以咸香酱汁。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "sweet and sour pork"
msgid_plural "sweet and sour pork"
msgstr[0] "糖醋猪肉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sweet and sour pork', 'str_pl': 'sweet and sour
#. pork'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Thick chunks of pork bathed in a tangy red glaze over sticky white rice."
msgstr "厚实的猪肉块裹着酸爽的红色酱汁，铺在黏糯的白米饭上。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "broccoli beef"
msgid_plural "broccoli beef"
msgstr[0] "西兰花牛肉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broccoli beef', 'str_pl': 'broccoli beef'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Slices of salty chewy beef mixed with broccoli florets doused with a savory "
"sauce over sticky white rice."
msgstr "咸香有嚼劲的牛肉片与西兰花混合，浇上咸香酱汁，铺在黏糯的白米饭上。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "kung pao chicken"
msgid_plural "kung pao chicken"
msgstr[0] "宫保鸡丁"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'kung pao chicken', 'str_pl': 'kung pao chicken'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Stir-fried tender chicken and chili pods in a spicy teriyaki sauce over "
"sticky white rice."
msgstr "嫩滑的鸡肉与辣椒快炒，佐以辛辣照烧酱，铺在黏糯的白米饭上。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "fortune cookie (empty)"
msgid_plural "fortune cookies (empty)"
msgstr[0] "幸运饼干（空的）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fortune cookie (empty)', 'str_pl': 'fortune
#. cookies (empty)'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A sweet, hard hollow pastry that normally has a fortune written on paper for"
" you. This one, however, does not."
msgstr "一种甜而硬的中空糕点，通常内含写有签文的纸条。但这个没有。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "chicken katsu"
msgid_plural "chicken katsu"
msgstr[0] "炸鸡排"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'chicken katsu', 'str_pl': 'chicken katsu'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A breaded deep-fried chicken cutlet."
msgstr "裹面包屑的油炸鸡排。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "rice bowl"
msgid_plural "rice bowls"
msgstr[0] "米饭碗"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'rice bowl'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Steamed white rice, veggies, and teriyaki pork in a convenient bowl."
msgstr "蒸白米饭、蔬菜和照烧猪肉，盛于方便的碗中。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'rice bowl'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Steamed white rice, veggies, and teriyaki chicken in a convenient bowl."
msgstr "蒸白米饭、蔬菜和照烧鸡肉，盛于方便的碗中。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'rice bowl'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Steamed white rice, veggies, and teriyaki beef in a convenient bowl."
msgstr "蒸白米饭、蔬菜和照烧牛肉，盛于方便的碗中。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'rice bowl'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Steamed white rice and veggies with teriyaki sauce in a convenient bowl."
msgstr "蒸白米饭和蔬菜，佐以照烧酱，盛于方便的碗中。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "moo shu pork"
msgid_plural "moo shu pork"
msgstr[0] "木须猪肉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'moo shu pork', 'str_pl': 'moo shu pork'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Pork tenderloin cutlets in a mild savory sauce flanked by long thin strips "
"of cabbage, broccoli, and carrots."
msgstr "猪里脊肉排佐以温和咸香酱汁，配以细长的白菜、西兰花和胡萝卜丝。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "szechwan shrimp"
msgid_plural "szechwan shrimp"
msgstr[0] "四川虾"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'szechwan shrimp', 'str_pl': 'szechwan shrimp'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Shrimp in a salty sauce served over sticky white rice."
msgstr "咸香酱汁烹制的虾，铺在黏糯的白米饭上。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "egg drop soup"
msgid_plural "egg drop soup"
msgstr[0] "蛋花汤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'egg drop soup', 'str_pl': 'egg drop soup'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Boiled chicken broth with beaten egg wisps throughout. This version has tiny"
" chunks of tofu and white pepper seasoning as well."
msgstr "煮沸的鸡汤中漂浮着打散的蛋丝。此版本还加入了小块豆腐和白胡椒调味。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "hot and sour soup"
msgid_plural "egg drop soup"
msgstr[0] "酸辣汤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hot and sour soup', 'str_pl': 'egg drop soup'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A relatively thick soup of veggies, pork broth, corn starch, white pepper, "
"and vinegar. Very good for you."
msgstr "相对浓稠的汤，内含蔬菜、猪肉汤、玉米淀粉、白胡椒和醋。对身体非常有益。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "yakisoba noodles"
msgid_plural "yakisoba noodles"
msgstr[0] "日式炒面"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'yakisoba noodles', 'str_pl': 'yakisoba noodles'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Thick oily buckwheat noodles with tender chunks of stir-fried vegetables and"
" chicken. Salty and delicious."
msgstr "油润的粗荞麦面，配以嫩炒蔬菜和鸡肉块。咸香可口。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "chicken noodle soup"
msgid_plural "chicken noodle soup"
msgstr[0] "鸡肉面条汤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'chicken noodle soup', 'str_pl': 'chicken noodle
#. soup'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"An especially thick, hearty chicken noodle soup with wide egg noodles, large"
" chunks of chicken, and hefty slices of veggies in a savory broth."
msgstr "一碗特别浓郁、丰盛的鸡肉面条汤，配有宽鸡蛋面、大块鸡肉和厚实的蔬菜片，汤底鲜美。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "chicken and sausage gumbo soup"
msgid_plural "chicken and sausage gumbo soup"
msgstr[0] "鸡肉香肠秋葵汤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'chicken and sausage gumbo soup', 'str_pl':
#. 'chicken and sausage gumbo soup'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Particularly thick slices of dark meat chicken and spicy andouille sausage "
"in a traditional rice and veggie gumbo. Has a kick to it!"
msgstr "传统米饭蔬菜秋葵汤中加入了特别厚实的黑肉鸡块和辛辣的安杜维尔香肠。口感劲爆！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "steak and potato soup"
msgid_plural "steak and potato soup"
msgstr[0] "牛排土豆汤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'steak and potato soup', 'str_pl': 'steak and
#. potato soup'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Tender cuts of sirloin steak and yukon gold potato chunks in a creamy white "
"stock."
msgstr "嫩切的西冷牛排和育空黄金土豆块，浸泡在奶油白汤中。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "venus de milo soup"
msgid_plural "venus de milo soup"
msgstr[0] "维纳斯德米洛汤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'venus de milo soup', 'str_pl': 'venus de milo
#. soup'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A New England specialty, Venus De Milo soup is thoroughly browned ground "
"beef, diced tomatoes, mixed veggies, and orzo in a beef and onion broth."
msgstr "新英格兰特色菜，维纳斯德米洛汤包含充分煎香的碎牛肉、番茄丁、混合蔬菜和米粒面，汤底为牛肉洋葱汤。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "old-fashioned chicken and dumplings soup"
msgid_plural "old-fashioned chicken and dumplings soup"
msgstr[0] "老式鸡肉饺子汤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'old-fashioned chicken and dumplings soup',
#. 'str_pl': 'old-fashioned chicken and dumplings soup'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A traditional New England preparation of the time-honored chicken and "
"dumplings. Packed full of delicious juices and flavor. The entire chicken is"
" used to make the initial stock, then removed, the meat is pulled off the "
"bones, and then dropped in with bay leaves, salt and pepper, and the puffy, "
"slightly sticky dumplings."
msgstr ""
"传统新英格兰风味的经典鸡肉饺子汤。充满美味的汤汁和风味。整只鸡用于制作初始汤底，然后取出，将肉从骨头上撕下，与月桂叶、盐、胡椒以及蓬松、略带粘性的饺子一起放入汤中。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "creamy crab bisque soup"
msgid_plural "creamy crab bisque soup"
msgstr[0] "奶油蟹肉浓汤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'creamy crab bisque soup', 'str_pl': 'creamy crab
#. bisque soup'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A New England icon, crab bisque is perfectly cooked-through crab meat in a "
"light, creamy broth with a balanced, flavorful blend of ground ginger and "
"minced garlic, carrot, green onion, celery heart, cayenne pepper, and dried "
"lemon peel."
msgstr "新英格兰标志性菜肴，蟹肉浓汤包含完美煮熟的蟹肉，汤底清淡奶油，融合了姜末、蒜末、胡萝卜、青葱、芹菜心、辣椒粉和干柠檬皮的平衡风味。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "firehouse chili"
msgid_plural "firehouse chili"
msgstr[0] "消防站辣椒汤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'firehouse chili', 'str_pl': 'firehouse chili'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A New England twist on an American staple, firehouse chili has a mix of 5 "
"different chopped, powdered, and crushed peppers, cinnamon, and cumin to "
"infuse the juicy tomato, onion, carrot, beans, and beef chunks with a "
"powerful kick. Has a little brown sugar to temper the flavor."
msgstr ""
"新英格兰风味的美国主食，消防站辣椒汤混合了5种不同的切碎、粉末和碾碎的辣椒、肉桂和孜然，为多汁的番茄、洋葱、胡萝卜、豆类和牛肉块注入强劲的辣味。加入少许红糖调和风味。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "beef stew"
msgid_plural "beef stew"
msgstr[0] "炖牛肉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'beef stew', 'str_pl': 'beef stew'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Beef stew done the New England way: slow-baked with fresh mushrooms, peas, "
"tomato soup, and red wine in addition to the usual potatoes, carrots, "
"onions, and chewy beef."
msgstr "新英格兰风味的炖牛肉：慢炖时加入新鲜蘑菇、豌豆、番茄汤和红酒，以及常见的土豆、胡萝卜、洋葱和有嚼劲的牛肉。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "New England clam chowder"
msgid_plural "New England clam chowder"
msgstr[0] "新英格兰蛤蜊浓汤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'New England clam chowder', 'str_pl': 'New
#. England clam chowder'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"This is a local take on the world-famous New England clam chowder. It uses "
"diced salted pork to boost the overall flavor."
msgstr "这是世界闻名的新英格兰蛤蜊浓汤的本地版本。使用咸猪肉丁来提升整体风味。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "13 bean good luck soup"
msgid_plural "13 bean good luck soup"
msgstr[0] "十三豆幸运汤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '13 bean good luck soup', 'str_pl': '13 bean good
#. luck soup'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A blend of multiple beans with ham, tomatoes, celery, onions, red bell "
"peppers and generous salt."
msgstr "多种豆类混合火腿、番茄、芹菜、洋葱、红甜椒和大量盐。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "classic clam chowder"
msgid_plural "classic clam chowder"
msgstr[0] "经典蛤蜊浓汤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'classic clam chowder', 'str_pl': 'classic clam
#. chowder'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"This is clam chowder the way you expect it. Creamy. White. Slightly chewy. "
"Great with crackers."
msgstr "这是你想象中的蛤蜊浓汤。奶油状。白色。略带嚼劲。搭配饼干非常美味。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "wild mushroom chowder"
msgid_plural "wild mushroom chowder"
msgstr[0] "野生蘑菇浓汤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wild mushroom chowder', 'str_pl': 'wild mushroom
#. chowder'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A mix of veggies, various wild mushrooms, and thick-cut bacon in a broth of "
"heavy cream, white wine, and chicken stock."
msgstr "混合蔬菜、各种野生蘑菇和厚切培根，汤底为浓奶油、白葡萄酒和鸡汤。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "gloucester fish chowder"
msgid_plural "gloucester fish chowder"
msgstr[0] "格洛斯特鱼浓汤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gloucester fish chowder', 'str_pl': 'gloucester
#. fish chowder'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Bite-sized chunks of just-through cooked hake in a creamy stock with thick "
"potato slices, chopped onions, thick chopped bacon, and a chopped bacon and "
"chive garnish. A regional specialty."
msgstr "一口大小的鳕鱼块，刚刚煮熟，浸泡在奶油汤中，配有厚土豆片、切碎的洋葱、厚切培根，以及培根和细香葱装饰。地方特色菜。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "seafood chowder"
msgid_plural "seafood chowder"
msgstr[0] "海鲜浓汤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'seafood chowder', 'str_pl': 'seafood chowder'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Succulent tiny shrimps. Chewy chopped clam. Delicate flaky haddock. Fried, "
"crumbled bacon. All in a creamy stock with thick chunks of veggies. This is "
"what made New England famous."
msgstr "多汁的小虾。有嚼劲的切碎蛤蜊。细腻易碎的鳕鱼。油炸、弄碎的培根。全部浸泡在奶油汤中，配有厚实的蔬菜块。这正是新英格兰闻名遐迩的菜肴。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "tofu (raw)"
msgid_plural "tofu (raw)"
msgstr[0] "豆腐（生的）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tofu (raw)', 'str_pl': 'tofu (raw)'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A block of extra-firm tofu, perfect for stir-frying. Not exactly palatable "
"raw."
