msgstr "重度加工的耐嚼巧克力饼干，夹着人工调味软糖馅料。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "oatmeal cream pie"
msgid_plural "oatmeal cream pies"
msgstr[0] "燕麦奶油派"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'oatmeal cream pie', 'str_pl': 'oatmeal cream
#. pies'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Heavily processed cream sandwiched between two artificially flavored oatmeal"
" cookies. A childhood favorite!"
msgstr "重度加工的奶油夹在两块人工调味的燕麦饼干之间。童年最爱！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "cosmic brownie"
msgid_plural "cosmic brownies"
msgstr[0] "宇宙布朗尼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cosmic brownie', 'str_pl': 'cosmic brownies'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Some of the richest, chewiest brownies you'll ever taste, topped with the "
"most colorful candy topping you'll ever see. Truly a rare treat."
msgstr "你尝过的最浓郁、最耐嚼的布朗尼之一，顶部覆盖着你见过的最多彩的糖果装饰。真是难得的享受。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "donut stick"
msgid_plural "donut sticks"
msgstr[0] "甜甜圈棒"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'donut stick', 'str_pl': 'donut sticks'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"The breakfast of champions for many young kids. Heavily processed and coated"
" with thick layers of artificial flavoring."
msgstr "许多小朋友的冠军早餐。重度加工，覆盖着厚厚的人工调味层。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "survivor cookie"
msgid_plural "survivor cookies"
msgstr[0] "幸存者饼干"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor cookie'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Improvised cookies, often made with non-standard ingredients. Their flavor "
"varies wildly from cookie to cookie as a result. Good in a pinch, but not "
"nearly as good as a commercial mix. Due to being made mostly with dry "
"ingredients, these keep for a long time."
msgstr ""
"临时制作的饼干，通常使用非标准原料。因此，每块饼干的味道差异极大。紧急情况下不错，但远不如商业混合品。由于主要由干原料制成，这些饼干能保存很长时间。"

#: .\containers.json
msgid "deli tray"
msgid_plural "deli trays"
msgstr[0] "熟食托盘"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'deli tray'}
#: .\containers.json
msgid ""
"A plastic deli tray with a fitted transparent plastic lid. Commonly used to "
"display and transport individual meals such as sandwiches and chow mein."
msgstr "一个塑料熟食托盘，配有合适的透明塑料盖。通常用于展示和运输单独餐点，如三明治和炒面。"

#: .\containers.json
msgid "deli platter"
msgid_plural "deli platters"
msgstr[0] "熟食拼盘"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'deli platter'}
#: .\containers.json
msgid ""
"A round plastic deli platter with a tall fitted transparent plastic lid. "
"Normally used for larger displays like cheesecake and samplers."
msgstr "一个圆形塑料熟食拼盘，配有高大的合适透明塑料盖。通常用于较大展示，如芝士蛋糕和样品拼盘。"

#: .\containers.json
msgid "rigid plastic case"
msgid_plural "rigid plastic cases"
msgstr[0] "硬质塑料箱"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'rigid plastic case'}
#: .\containers.json
msgid ""
"A large, rigid plastic case normally used to store 30 day emergency food "
"supplies or cat litter."
msgstr "一个大型硬质塑料箱，通常用于储存30天应急食品或猫砂。"

#: .\containers.json
msgid "plastic tub"
msgid_plural "plastic tubs"
msgstr[0] "塑料桶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'plastic tub'}
#: .\containers.json
