"dry powder."
msgstr "一个广口塑料桶，配有旋盖。通常用于储存干粉。"

#: .\containers.json
msgid "large plastic cup"
msgid_plural "large plastic cups"
msgstr[0] "大塑料杯"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'large plastic cup'}
#: .\containers.json
msgid ""
