"holding individual deli soup and salad servings."
msgstr "一个透明塑料杯，广口并配有合适的盖子。通常用于盛装单独的熟食汤和沙拉份餐。"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Gourmand's Graces"
msgstr "美食家的恩赐"

#. ~ Description for Gourmand's Graces
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Greatly expands the selection of various cooked food you can find in grocery"
" stores and pharmacy fridges. Focuses on items you'd expect to find in "
"bakery and deli departments."
msgstr "极大地扩展了你在杂货店和药店冰箱中可以找到的各种熟食选择。专注于你期望在烘焙区和熟食区找到的物品。"

